"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-06-a-green-card-mean-athletics-olympics-21370255\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The athletics is in full swing at theParis2024Olympics, with the biggest stars in track and fieldeyeing glory at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sport is amongst the most popular of any Games, and those tuning in to watch from the comfort of their own sofas may have noticed a green card being issued to athletes at the start of some races.\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A green card is one of several cards which can be given to athletes during competition, but what are the meanings behind them?\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow\\u00a0Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Here is everything you need to know.\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If athletes are recalled following a faulty start but no competitor was at fault, such as when there is an issue with the machine used to catch false starts, then the whole field will be given a green card.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes are sent back to the starting blocks and the race is restarted.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes are shown a yellow card if they are adjudged to have caused the start of a race to be aborted.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The issuing of the card is used to signify that an athlete has been handed a personal warning for improper conduct.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Examples of this include sitting up in the blocks, holding their hand up, deliberately delaying the start or making a noise.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Should the athlete commit another offence, they will be shown a red card and subsequently disqualified.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The diagonal red and black card is given to athletes when a false start has been made, disqualifying them from the race.\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A false start is defined when an athlete moves before, or within 0.1 seconds, of the starting gun.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Previously, a false start would result in a warning for the entire field, with any resultant false start seeing the athlete at fault disqualified.\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The rules have now changed, however, with one false start resulting in instant disqualification.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An athlete can protest against the disqualification or run under protest, with the disqualification reviewed at the end of the race.\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Whale joins Olympic surfers during semi final in Tahiti  ArrowMORE:BBC commentator slams 'unbelievably bad riding' that 'spooked' horse at the Olympics  ArrowMORE:Olympic pole vaulter offered $250,000 porn deal after going viral at Paris Games  Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9986592754103785, \"rank\": 0.0012469005182748705, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\",